    - target: {fileID: 8118535028943774260, guid: f91b012845cb94e4782783ecf550840e, type: 3}
      propertyPath: m_Name
      value: DummyChat (5)
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 8514466214802780656, guid: f91b012845cb94e4782783ecf550840e, type: 3}
      propertyPath: m_text
      value: 'The Ministry of Eternal Revenue has received numerous complaints stating
        that since the onset of the zombie outbreak, human fear has shifted toward
        the roaming undead rather than our spectral citizens. We acknowledge that
        daily Fear Point generation has hit a record low, causing many ghosts to
        default on their tax obligations.

        However, all matters regarding
        the Fear Point Tax must proceed as mandated, regardless of external circumstances.
        The Hell Administration will not accept tax delinquencies under any pretext
        or excuse.

        Therefore, let this serve as a final reminder: any citizen
        with outstanding Fear Point debts will be granted a strict one-month grace
        period. If payment is still not rendered by the deadline, the delinquent
        ghost will be immediately deported back to Hell and reassigned to the manual
        labor sectors.

'
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 8592897770337388089, guid: f91b012845cb94e4782783ecf550840e, type: 3}
      propertyPath: m_text
      value: '[OFFICIAL ANNOUNCEMENT FROM THE UNDERWORLD COUNCIL]'
