    - target: {fileID: 7012656115409611875, guid: 603cc30f40edb6943b3717f239c4ca01, type: 3}
      propertyPath: m_text
      value: Zombie mutation just made me homeless. These stupid bugs are eating
        my structural steel and I have nowhere to sleep.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 7012656115409611875, guid: 603cc30f40edb6943b3717f239c4ca01, type: 3}
