    - target: {fileID: 8514466214802780656, guid: f91b012845cb94e4782783ecf550840e, type: 3}
      propertyPath: m_text
      value: hi guys~ umm so ik we're all super broke because of the zombie outbreak...
        but hear me out! why don't we just... get rid of those zombies? ik ik, we're
        ghosts and zombies are a human problem. like, why should we even help humans,
        right? absolutely not!! but... if the zombies disappear, maybe humans will
        finally fear US again? and i can go back to scaring them? no? okay back to
        lurking~
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
